,[61,1418,1419],{},"Workers 和 Pages",[84,1421,1422,1423,1426,1427],{},"點 ",[61,1424,1425],{},"建立"," > ",[61,1428,1429],{},"建立 Worker",[84,1431,1432,1433],{},"名稱隨便取，像是 ",[222,1434,1435],{},"agent-readiness",[84,1437,1438],{},"點「部署」先用預設程式碼部署上去",[84,1440,1441],{},"部署完之後點「編輯程式碼」，把你的 Worker 腳本貼上去",[84,1443,1444],{},"點右上角「部署」",[12,1446,1447],{},"部署完之後還要設定路由，告訴 Cloudflare 哪些請求要經過這個 Worker：",[293,1449,1450,1453,1459,1466],{},[84,1451,1452],{},"回到你的 domain 的管理頁面",[84,1454,1455,1456],{},"左邊選 ",[61,1457,1458],{},"Workers 路由",[84,1460,1461,1462,1465],{},"新增路由，路由填 ",[222,1463,1464],{},"yourdomain.com\u002F*","，Worker 選你剛剛建的那個",[84,1467,1468],{},"儲存",[12,1470,1471,1472,1475],{},"另外你可以把 Worker 的 ",[222,1473,1474],{},"workers.dev"," 公開網址關掉，因為它只需要透過路由綁定就好，不需要有自己的公開入口。",[1477,1478,1479],"blockquote",{},[12,1480,1481,1484],{},[61,1482,1483],{},"Note","\n你可能會擔心 Cloudflare Worker 免費版一天只有 10 萬次請求會不會不夠用，但以一般技術部落格來說，一天大概幾百到幾千次瀏覽量，連免費額度的 1% 都用不到，完全不用擔心。",[19,1486,1488],{"id":1487},"最終結果100-分滿分","最終結果：100 分滿分",[12,1490,1491],{},"全部修完之後重新掃描，結果：",[81,1493,1494,1500,1506,1512,1518],{},[84,1495,1496,1499],{},[61,1497,1498],{},"Discoverability","：100（3\u002F3）",[84,1501,1502,1505],{},[61,1503,1504],{},"Content","：100（1\u002F1）",[84,1507,1508,1511],{},[61,1509,1510],{},"Bot Access Control","：100（2\u002F2）",[84,1513,1514,1517],{},[61,1515,1516],{},"API, Auth, MCP & Skill Discovery","：100（6\u002F6）",[84,1519,1520,1523],{},[61,1521,1522],{},"總分：100 分，Level 5 Agent-Native"," 🎉",[12,1525,1526],{},"整理一下最終每項的解法：",[1528,1529,1530,1543],"table",{},[1531,1532,1533],"thead",{},[1534,1535,1536,1540],"tr",{},[1537,1538,1539],"th",{},"項目",[1537,1541,1542],{},"怎麼解的",[1544,1545,1546,1554,1560,1566,1576,1583,1589,1596],"tbody",{},[1534,1547,1548,1551],{},[1549,1550,88],"td",{},[1549,1552,1553],{},"本來就有",[1534,1555,1556,1558],{},[1549,1557,94],{},[1549,1559,1553],{},[1534,1561,1562,1564],{},[1549,1563,127],{},[1549,1565,1553],{},[1534,1567,1568,1570],{},[1549,1569,133],{},[1549,1571,1572,1573],{},"robots.txt 加一行 ",[222,1574,1575],{},"Content-Signal",[1534,1577,1578,1580],{},[1549,1579,100],{},[1549,1581,1582],{},"Cloudflare 回應標頭轉換規則",[1534,1584,1585,1587],{},[1549,1586,112],{},[1549,1588,354],{},[1534,1590,1591,1593],{},[1549,1592,178],{},[1549,1594,1595],{},"HTML 裡面加一段 JavaScript",[1534,1597,1598,1601],{},[1549,1599,1600],{},".well-known 五個檔案",[1549,1602,1603],{},"全部用 Cloudflare Worker 處理",[19,1605,1606],{"id":1606},"補充注意事項",[293,1608,1609,1618],{},[84,1610,1611,1614,1615,1617],{},[61,1612,1613],{},"GitHub Pages 不支援 .well-known 目錄","：即使放了 ",[222,1616,820],{}," 也沒用，需要用 Cloudflare Worker 來服務這些檔案",[84,1619,1620,1623],{},[61,1621,1622],{},"Markdown Negotiation 需要 Worker","：靜態網站本身沒辦法做內容協商，需要靠 Cloudflare Worker 來處理",[19,1625,1626],{"id":1626},"結論",[12,1628,1629],{},"整個修下來其實不複雜，大部分項目都是加個檔案或加個設定就搞定了，最花時間的反而是在踩坑跟除錯。",[12,1631,1632],{},"不過說老實話，這個評測工具有些項目（像是 OAuth）對純部落格來說真的沒什麼實際意義，單純就是為了拿分，但 Discoverability 跟 Content 那幾項倒是蠻值得做的。畢竟 AI Agent 的生態只會越來越成熟，提早把這些基礎建設做好，你的內容被 AI 正確存取跟引用的機會也會更高哩～",[1634,1635,1636],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .sj_SG, html code.shiki .sj_SG{--shiki-default:#DBB7FF}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF